summary:
Geologist with experience as exploration and development geoscientist in the petroleum and geothermal energy industry. Hard-working, responsible, eager to learn and enthusiastic. Good communication and organisation skills.

Technical skills include:
- Seismic interpretation and time-depth conversion
- Mapping, well correlation and 3D static modelling
- Petrophysics (basic)
- Well planning and operations geology
